sprykerComponent.name: filter-range
sprykerComponent.readme:
Enables manual filtering by the price range with minimum and maximum values.

Code sample

{% include molecule('filter-range', 'CatalogPage') with {
     data: {
         parameter: parameter,
         min: min,
         activeMin: activeMin,
         max: max,
         activeMax: activeMax
     }
 } only %}

defines.name: data
defines.contract:
{
    parameter: required,
    min: required,
    activeMin: required,
    max: required,
    activeMax: required
}
